name: Ice Punch
summary: Deals damage, and has a 10% chance of freezing the opponent.
viability: There aren't many physical Ice type moves out there, so this will have to do for many Pokemon. Feraligatr gets a noticeable boost with Sheer Force, making it a great coverage move for Grass types. The same can be said for Pokemon like Conkeldurr and Lopunny, who need a good coverage move. It's not a bad move at all, but lacks a bit of power.
